parameters: \C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(I feel a strong magical power...
\n<Bray>Tch, you've followed me all the way here!

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Hey Rain, you made it this far. Impressive that
you managed to escape from there.

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Well, I had a feeling you would come. That's why
I've been protecting the device like this.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>But why can't you just behave? Even though I've
taken the drugs and all. How many times do you
have to interfere with us until you're satisfied?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>That's my line. As long as you all continue to
disrupt the peace of the people, I will stand in
your way no matter how many times!

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>I see... Well then, let me ask you this, Rain. Are
you determined to destroy this device and not
become my woman?
\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>I see... Well then, I guess there's no helping it.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>It's not just because of my promise with Demon. I
can't let this be destroyed either.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>And besides, I absolutely want to make you mine.
As a thief, I won't be satisfied until I obtain
what I desire.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>This time, I'll do it seriously to fulfill my
desires!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────That's my line...! \.Don't think it'll go the
same way as our match!!
I'll kill everyone! \.\ Let's go, oraah!!

\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>───With this, all the magical devices should be
destroyed...! All that's left is to defeat Demon
himself────────

\N<Caldo>I came to provide support since we've already
completed the takeover of the club, but it seems
like it's already finished.

\OC[31]\N<Rain>Yes, let's destroy the last magical device and the
leader of 'Dark Owl' should be there...

\CE[79]\N<Caldo>I see, good job Rain-san. I'll take care of the
escort.

\CE[93]\OC[30]\N<Phils>Amazing! So, with this, all the evil magic will
disappear, right?

\OC[5] No, it won't disappear that easily, you
know?

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>I never expected all four devices to be destroyed.
You're quite impressive.

\OC[5]\N<Dimon>I thought I could rely on Buster- san, but he
wasn't as useful as I thought. I never expected to
be defeated like this by just one person.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>─────With this, the plan to take over Hakudeti has
been crushed. \. Now, I just have to defeat
you...!

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>You said it yourself when we first met, didn't
you? That this city is already too late. But none
of my plans have been affected at all.

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>You're just putting on a brave front... I've
destroyed all the devices emitting 'Nightmare
Heaven'. I shouldn't be able to control the people
of this city anymore...!

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>─────Hmm, it seems like you're misunderstanding
something.

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>The four magical devices are nothing more than
auxiliary devices for the main body. After all,
the target is a wide range. They were installed as
subsidiary units to efficiently cast spells, like
sub-devices.

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>I am the one who is casting this magic! Unless I
stop using it or get killed, 'Nightmare Heaven'
won't stop, you know!?

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>Although the efficiency has decreased due to the
destruction of the subsidiary devices, it seems
that the magic has already spread sufficiently in
this area. The members of 'Nightmare Heaven' have
played their role as a time-buying measure,
haven't they?

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>Oh no, that's really barbaric. There's no need to
expose yourself in front of the enemy like that,
it's just an illusion.

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>Hmm... Now all that's left is to wait for
'Nightmare Heaven' to fully permeate... But to
ensure everything goes smoothly, you're quite a
hindrance, Rain-san.

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>Since you're going to resist until the end anyway,
let's settle this decisively.

\OC[5]\N<Dimon>I will prepare an entrance to my hideout at the
summit of Mount Gorio, located north of Hakudeti.
Come alone.

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>Well, of course, that's if you have the courage to
come!

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>───This is what I desire! I will defeat you... and
protect this town!

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>I'm looking forward to it. Make sure to prepare
yourself without any regrets. Take as much time as
you like. After all, the more you wait, the more
this town will be deeply dyed by my magic.

\CE[94]\OC[5]\N<Dimon>Well then, goodbye, you insignificant insects.
Kuhahaha!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>───... Anyway, let's return to the surface for
now. We need to put these two in prison...

\CE[94]\OC[30]\N<Phils>We must also call Lord Fristo and have a
conversation.............

Will you fight against the resurrected dungeon
boss? *After defeating it, it will revive again
after one day.

\N<Thief Leader>I'm sorry, Boss... Having such allies was beyond
my expectations...

\N<Thief Leader>─────No, you've come back well. If you had also
been caught, I wouldn't have known about that
woman called Meryl either.

\N<Thief Leader>For those who got caught... well, it shouldn't be
a problem. They shouldn't have any significant
information.

\N<Thief Leader>I'll have you move again, who directly confronted
them. First, heal your injuries. Once you
understand that, you can go.

\N<Thief Leader>Well then... instead of leaving everything to the
people below and Dimon's husband, maybe it's about
time I also went to meet this person called Rain.

\N<Thief Leader>She seems like quite the attractive woman, I'm
looking forward to it. Hehe...
